I'm confused.  Aren't ALL MMORPG's leveling treadmills? It depends on your perspective.  I think it all comes down to perspective. If you look at leveling as a job you MUST do as fast as you can its not gonna be fun.  If you relax, enjoy and let it come its not a treadmill at all but a natural progression. <p>Silverleaf Goldenthorn<BR>
